                            <comment id="279555" author="adilger" created="Mon, 14 Sep 2020 20:09:32 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;The new sanity-quota test_1g added by patch &lt;a href=&quot;https://review.whamcloud.com/39469/&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://review.whamcloud.com/39469/&lt;/a&gt; &quot;&lt;tt&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-13810&quot; title=&quot;Check OST pool quota hard limit at file with wide striping&quot; class=&quot;issue-link&quot; data-issue-key=&quot;LU-13810&quot;&gt;&lt;del&gt;LU-13810&lt;/del&gt;&lt;/a&gt; tests: OST Pool Quotas with wide striping&lt;/tt&gt;&quot; has been failing on ZFS backends intermittently (8 of 54 ZFS runs) since it landed on 2020-09-08:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt; &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/49b044e9-1d40-428a-bdda-d7b5dfb62334&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/49b044e9-1d40-428a-bdda-d7b5dfb62334&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/4661c4a3-d89a-4206-8d2f-2f7d416b9110&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/4661c4a3-d89a-4206-8d2f-2f7d416b9110&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/a8b921c1-b374-4543-84fc-5830a16ac170&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/a8b921c1-b374-4543-84fc-5830a16ac170&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/7d7cb3c4-43dc-4e77-99b0-a1beaf2017c9&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/7d7cb3c4-43dc-4e77-99b0-a1beaf2017c9&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/ac017c85-dc4e-4acb-ab99-0bbfa55a95a2&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/ac017c85-dc4e-4acb-ab99-0bbfa55a95a2&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/dec47265-9311-4e88-9494-b895b50f8154&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/dec47265-9311-4e88-9494-b895b50f8154&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/e5ab75a4-435d-4aed-8508-097b712d51fa&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/e5ab75a4-435d-4aed-8508-097b712d51fa&lt;/a&gt;&lt;br/&gt;
 &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/3106dfa3-0aa4-42a9-bfd2-f8555ea2716e&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/sub_tests/3106dfa3-0aa4-42a9-bfd2-f8555ea2716e&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;I guess it is some kind of race with deleting files from the previous test or possibly the interaction between two different quota limits?&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;In any case, we need to get a fix or &lt;tt&gt;ALWAYS_EXCEPT&lt;/tt&gt; for ZFS or revert the patch.&lt;/p&gt;
